UNITED STATES of America ex rel. CHIN CHEUNG NAI, Next Friend of Wong Bak Sun, Relator-Appellant, v. Edward CORSI, Commissioner of Immigration at the Port of New York, Respondent-Appellee. No. 342. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. April 3, 1933. James C. Thomas, of New York City, for appellant. George Z. Medalie, U. S. Atty., of New York City (Ira Koenig, Asst. U. S. Atty., of New York City, of counsel), for appellee.

Before MANTON, L HAND, and SWAN, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Order [55 F.(2d) 360] affirmed.
